snippet.title: SWORD ART ONLINE: ALICIZATION LYCORIS - Key Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Your journey with #SAO continues in The Underworld! Learn about the battle system, character customization, multi-player, and more!

WATCH our latest trailer for #SwordArtOnline: #AlicizationLycoris and prepare for its arrival on May 22nd, 2020! Pre-order: https://bandainam.co/SAOAL
